WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:02.466
No, I didn't.

2
00:00:02.533 --> 00:00:05.000
Please believe me. You're still lying to me

3
00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:06.766
You think I'm a fool

4
00:00:07.966 --> 00:00:09.266
I have investigated

5
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:10.866
Wang Yuan is your stepmother

6
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:13.133
You've hated your dad since he died

7
00:00:13.133 --> 00:00:14.333
So you used me for revenge?

8
00:00:14.333 --> 00:00:15.666
Who gave you the courage?

9
00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:18.233
Exactly.

10
00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:20.700
I want to use you

11
00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:23.666
Because Wang Yu always troubles me.

12
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.433
I can't resist

13
00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:28.233
I want to beg for your protection

14
00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:30.566
The whole house.

15
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.900
Only you would stand up to protect me

16
00:00:38.333 --> 00:00:41.966
It was the first time I felt protected.

17
00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:44.900
If you think I lied to you

18
00:00:45.566 --> 00:00:47.266
Then you will kill me.

19
00:00:48.700 --> 00:00:50.900
I would rather die at your hands

20
00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:53.666
I don't want to be given up by you either.

21
00:00:54.533 --> 00:00:57.066
Ok don't cry

22
00:00:57.500 --> 00:00:58.700
Tell me about it

23
00:01:08.266 --> 00:01:10.000
Uncle don't

24
00:01:10.333 --> 00:01:12.266
What if my aunt comes back?

25
00:01:12.366 --> 00:01:14.700
Don't worry. He's out of town.

26
00:01:14.700 --> 00:01:15.966
Come back tomorrow

27
00:01:20.933 --> 00:01:23.566
I'd like to see Chen Lin, this little bitch hoof

28
00:01:23.566 --> 00:01:26.466
How big of a splash can you make at your neighbor's house?

